<h2 id="faq">❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>Is 1v1.LOL free to play?</h3><p>Yes, the browser version is completely free. There are optional cosmetic purchases in the shop, but they don't affect gameplay.</p></div>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>Can I play 1v1.LOL on mobile?</h3><p>Yes, it's available on iOS and Android with touch controls. The browser version works on desktop and some tablets.</p></div>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>What's the difference between 1v1.LOL and JustBuild.LOL?</h3><p>JustBuild is a practice mode within 1v1.LOL focused purely on building — no combat, no timer. It's where you warm up and refine your construction skills before competitive matches.</p></div>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>How do I unlock new characters?</h3><p>There are 11 unique champions you can unlock through the shop or by collecting boxes earned through gameplay.</p></div>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>What's the best weapon combo?</h3><p>AR + Shotgun is the most versatile for most situations. AR handles mid-range pressure, Shotgun finishes close-range fights. Sniper users need precision but can one-shot from distance.</p></div>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>How long do matches last?</h3><p>Typical matches last 5-10 minutes. The zone shrinks to force confrontations, so games don't drag on. Perfect for quick sessions.</p></div>

<h2>📝 Conclusion</h2>
<p>1v1.LOL nails the building + shooting formula in a streamlined browser package. The skill ceiling is high — mastering 90s, peek-shots, and weapon switching takes practice — but that's what makes victories so satisfying. Whether you're warming up for Fortnite or just want quick competitive action, this game delivers.</p>
<p><strong>Ready to build and battle?</strong> Jump into 1v1.LOL and see if you can outbuild and outshoot your opponent!</p>
